<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-09-08T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-09-08T14:00:00-05:00" n="692" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d692">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">861a.01/69: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Consul at Vladivostok</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Macgowan</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-09-08T15:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">September 8,
                                        1921—3 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>Your 96 September 3rd, 2 p.m. evidently refers to the present Vladivostok
                            Government, while Departments September 1, 6 p.m. refers to former
                            Vladivostok Government.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>